CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier reads:" Found Most Eggs- Newell Hall, 7535 Bennett Street, Homewood, is shown with a portion of his catch after he found the most eggs at the Y's Men's Club Easter Egg Hunt at the Centre Avenue YMCA. His extreme delight is shown in expression on his face."
TitMainTitle: Newell Hall holding eggs from Centre Avenue YMCA easter egg hunt and leaning against pool table
